A simple ruby-script based on Tim Popes' Pathogen for easy updating vim-plugins in compliance with the yaml-config.

Prerequisites:
- ruby, rubygems
- gems rubyzip and minitar

Install:
  gem install rubyzip archive-tar-minitar
  mv ~/.vim ~/.vim.orig
  git clone git@github.com:hariton/pathogenized.git ~/.vim
  cp ./config/plugins.yml.example ./config/plugins.yml

Using:
  edit ~/.vim/config/plugins.yml
  run ~/.vim/bin/update_plugins
